title: Level

claims.preamble: The ornamental design of a level, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is an isometric view of a level incorporating our new design, wherein portions of the level are shown in phantom and form no part of the claimed design, and wherein portions of the level that are broken indicate indeterminate length;
FIG. 2 is a left side elevation view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a top plan view thereof;
FIG. 4 is an end elevation view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a right side elevation view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 7 is an opposite end elevation view thereof.
